<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Purchase</title>
</head>
<body>
<div>
        <h1 style="margin: 10px 0">E-Commerce App</h1>
        <hr>
        <h2>Tu compra {{id}} se encuentra en proceso de preparaci√≥n</h2>
        <p>Gracias por comprar en e-commerce app, en breve nos comunicaremos...</p>
        <br>
        <h3>Detalle de tu compra</h3>
        <p>Fecha: {{purchase_datetime}}</p>
        <p>Code: {{code}}</p>
        <hr>
        <br>
        <h4 style ="background-color: aliceblue;" >Productos</h4>
        <table style="width: 100%;">
            <tr>
                <th style = "text-align: left;" >Item</th>
                <th style = "text-align: left;" >Price</th>
                <th style = "text-align: left;" >Quantity</th>
                <th style = "text-align: left;" >Total</th>
            </tr>
            {{#each products}}
            {{#with this}}
                <tr >
                    <td>{{title}}</td>
                    <td>{{price}}</td>
                    <td>{{quantity}}</td>
                    <td>${{total}}</td>
                </tr>
            {{/with}}
            {{/each}}
            <tr style = "margin-top: 15px;">
                <td style = "font-weight: bold; font-size: 1rem;">Total</td>
                <td> </td>
                <td> </td>
                <td style = "font-weight: bold; font-size: 1rem;">${{amount}}</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
</div>

</body>
</html>
